name: Swerved
overview: WWE teams up with the Director of Jackass and Bad Grandpa, Jeff Tremaine, to give you the hilarious original series, Swerved.

seasons.name: Season 2
seasons.overview: WWE reunites with the director of “Jackass” and “Bad Grandpa,” Jeff Tremaine, for a second season of the hilarious WWE original series Swerved!

episodes.name: I Thought I Was Dead
episodes.overview: Zack Ryder and Alex Riley get shocked, Booker T gets Hornswoggled, and we take the Poo Mic to the WWE Hall of Fame Red Carpet.

episodes.name: Are You Crazy Fox?
episodes.overview: R-Truth gets a lesson in gym safety, a frisky granny invades Axxess and Kofi locks the champ out of Extreme Rules.

episodes.name: Are You Pranking Me?
episodes.overview: R-Truth is a Bad Ass Elephant, Fandango treats Heath Slater and The Ascension to lunch and Kofi and Xavier get into an all out prank war.

episodes.name: You Little Punk
episodes.overview: Curtis Axel gets shot down by a bratty kid. Byron and Summer Rae help an old lady. Fandango and Heath Slater create chaos in a coffee shop.

episodes.name: The Boogeyman Is Real
episodes.overview: Boogeyman and Big Show experience technical difficulties, Rosa’s patience gets tested, and Superstars sit down for a stinky lunch.

episodes.name: You Swerved Yourself
episodes.overview: Rosa and Foxy meet a sleazeball dad and his loudmouth kid. Zack Ryder helps a pregnant woman. Heath Slater gets treated to a messy 3D TV.

episodes.name: Thank You For Swerving Us
episodes.overview: Superstars seek revenge! Paige gets a cattle prod. Adam Rose deals with a saucy fan. Superstars and Divas remember their favorite Swerves.

episodes.name: Who Woulda Thought?
episodes.overview: Swerved is back! Miz pranks a security guard, a focus group samples some New Day products, and Paige makes a bloody mess.

episodes.name: You've Been Had All Day
episodes.overview: Big Show becomes a bronze statue, a crazy fan invades the Performance Center, Becky Lynch and R-Truth set up a security checkpoint.

episodes.name: Drop It Down!
episodes.overview: Rollins and Orton surprise trash-talking kids, The New Day and Usos cause chaos in a hardware store, and R-Truth is a crazy ex-boyfriend

episodes.name: Don't Have A Face For TV
episodes.overview: Dean Ambrose and Renee Young play Prize Time, Usos pull some twin magic, Lana and Foxy get their makeup done, Stardust invades Axxess.

episodes.name: Can't Find Good Help
episodes.overview: Mr. McMahon goes deep undercover, Big E is a bad trainer, a Baby Elephant and Box Man team up to scare fans at Axxess.

episodes.name: You Said Booty
episodes.overview: Summer Rae takes surprising fan photos, Miz and Dolph have some awful auditions, and Charlotte locks Ric Flair out of the venue.

episodes.name: Having Hair Looks Stupid
episodes.overview: Kids make crazy signs with AJ Styles and Ryback, Social Outcasts secure a parking lot, and the Dudley Boyz have plumbing problems.

episodes.name: Dude, Are You Crazy?
episodes.overview: Mark Henry's on TV, Dolph and Paige go on dates, Tyler Breeze and Becky Lynch invade an art gallery, Neville and Booker T get interviewed.
